bert geoffrey achong ( born december 6 , 1928 port of spain , trinidad ; died november 20 , 1996 ) was a trinidadian and tobagonian of chinese descent   is best known for co - discovering the epstein - barr virus through use of electron microscopy .

name your disease : a virus that causes mono is known by these hyphenated names , but bert achong helped isolate it with them in 1964

epstein - barr